From ab301ebf799b4dbddb1351d77da49b2e6e1cf8ec Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Luca Boccassi <bluca@debian.org>
Date: Sat, 13 Jun 2020 15:09:39 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Problem: mtrie use of non-tail recursion leads to stack
 overflow

Solution: convert add and rm functions to iterative algorithms
---
 src/generic_mtrie.hpp      |  35 +-
 src/generic_mtrie_impl.hpp | 732 +++++++++++++++++++++----------------
 2 files changed, 436 insertions(+), 331 deletions(-)

